"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guimenuitem>मुद्रणं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Print the contents of the currently visible page. Handbooks in <acronym>PDF</"
"acronym> format you find on the <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/index.php?"
"language=en\"> &kde; Documentation Server</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"सम्प्रति दृश्यमानस्य पृष्ठस्य सामग्रीं मुद्रयन्तु । <acronym>PDF</acronym> प्रारूपेण "
"हस्तपुस्तिकाः भवन्तः <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/index.php?language=en\"> "
"&kde; प्रलेखनसर्वरः</ulink> इति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
