"उपमेनूवस्तूनि योजयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "सेटिंग्स्"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Fonts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>फॉन्ट् विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to configure the font family and size used by &khelpcenter;."
msgstr "&khelpcenter; द्वारा उपयुज्यमानं font family तथा size विन्यस्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &khelpcenter; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"अतिरिक्तरूपेण &khelpcenter; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा "
"<guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /"
